divs: Sighting DetailsAt 11:00 P.M. I went out on my balcony and saw little orange balls of light flying across the sky very fast. Then I saw a big V-shaped craft appear out of thin air and go across the sky very slowly.
Object Flight Path: Hovering then path,Path with directional change
Summary: Orbs over lake followed by V-shape very low
